"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1.jpg\" alt=\"puerto viejo best things to do punta uva beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"puerto viejo best things to do punta uva beach\" class=\"wp-image-76073 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15205250\/puerto-viejo-punta-uva-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>All drivers must provide a valid driver&#x2019;s license, a passport including a valid tourist visa stamp, and a credit card to make the payment and hold the deposit. An international driver&#x2019;s license is not required in Costa Rica unless your driver&#x2019;s license is not in Roman script.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/85619&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10124615\/car-rental-costarica-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10124615\/car-rental-costarica-1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10124615\/car-rental-costarica-1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Renting a Car in Costa Rica in 2022: All you need to know\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There are often random checkpoints by the traffic police, where you&#x2019;ll be asked to show your driver&#x2019;s license and ID. Try to keep these with you when driving the car. Note that your passport must have an entry stamp into the country that is not more than three months old.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11.jpg\" alt=\"driving rental car costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"driving rental car costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-77053 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha