 your car and expect to pay an additional 10 &#x2013; 30 USD per day on top of the advertised price. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21.jpg\" alt=\"fruits costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"fruits costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78891 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-rica-21-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22144058\/camping-costa-r