 for after.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--insurance \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--insurance\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/carrental-travel-insurance-heymondo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get a travel insurance for your trip<\/a> because it covers costs for a stolen or damaged rental car or in case of an accident.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>To get the insurance, most agencies require a credit card that has enough credit on it to cover the rental costs as well as the deposit hold. The deposit is an &#x2018;authorization only&#x2019; transaction that doesn&#x2019;t charge your card unless in the event of damage to the car. The exact number of the deposit depends on the type of insurance you select. For example, if you only purchase mandatory insurance, your deposit might be much higher than in the case you purchase full-coverage insurance.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Flat tires are not covered under any of the insurances &#x2013; you&#x2019;ll need to change it yourself and get a new spare tire at the rental office.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica la fortuna\"><\/noscript><img width=\"238\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica la fortuna\" class=\"wp-image-73886 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2.jpg 1353w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-423x600.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-571x810.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-238x338.jpg 238w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-541x768.jpg 541w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-722x1024.jpg 722w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-761x1080.jpg 761w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-1015x1440.jpg 1015w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-300x426.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-600x851.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.sa