iv>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Safety of driving in Costa Rica<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Driving in Costa Rica is a fantastic experience, it is perfectly safe and not chaotic at all. In the 9 weeks that we were there, we didn&#x2019;t have any situations on the road. Many of the roads have drastically improved over the last few years, and apart from a few potholes here and there, most of them are well paved. As long as you drive cautiously as you would in any other country, you&#x2019;ll be fine. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica driving\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"308\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica driving\" class=\"wp-image-74789 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-800x547.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-1080x738.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-450x308.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-263x180.jpg 263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224752\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-23-768x525.jpg 768w, 