ds are good to drive on and only consist of some potholes and higher (speed)bumps. The most popular destinations like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">La Fortuna<\/a> are, therefore, easily reached by any type of car.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/costa-rica-3-week-itinerary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ultimate 3-week Costa Rica Itinerary<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10111843\/car-rental-costa-rica-2.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-87272 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10111843\/car-rental-costa-rica-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10111843\/car-rental-costa-rica-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10111843\/car-rental-costa-rica-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/10111843\/car-rental-costa-rica-2