rides more comfortable on the lesser maintained gravel roads; however, choosing a standard car is more than worth it if you stick to the main roads. The cost for a regular car might be half the price of an SUV or 4&#xD7;4 vehicle. While you don&#x2019;t need to rent a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/camping-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">4&#xD7;4 in C<\/a>osta Rica, getting a car with some clearance from the ground is recommended. That way, you&#x2019;ll feel comfortable driving over potholes without the extra costs of a 4&#xD7;4.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica bridge\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica bridge\" class=\"wp-image-77055 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1428px) 100vw, 1428px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12.jpg 1428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-446x600.jpg 446w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-602x810.jpg 602w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185917\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-12-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/s