"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li>You can&#x2019;t count on road signs for navigation. As mentioned before, signs might be difficult to see, or they&#x2019;re non-existent. A good navigation system and an offline map are typically best. The Waze app is a good option as it&#x2019;s community-based and updated by locals in real-time.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica navigation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rent a car in costa rica navigation\" class=\"wp-image-76234 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/16181948\/puerto-viejo-town-7.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li>Finding parking won&#x2019;t be an issue as almost all restaurants and hotels have a parking lot. The only place you might have to pay for parking is at some national parks. Often there&#x2019;ll be a park guide to help you park &#x2013; make sure to tip him for the help!<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>If you get a fine, you won&#x2019;t have to pay it on the spot with the traffic officer but at the rental agency once you drop off the car. Make sure to do this as there is a law that can prohibit you from exiting the country if you don&#x2019;t.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li>Rental cars can&#x2019;t be taken across the international borders into Panama or Nicaragua. You can, sometimes, drop one car off at the agency in Costa Rica and pick up a new car on the other side for a fee.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14.jpg\" alt=\"surf costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"surf costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-76309 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/17024511\/puerto-viejo-town-14-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https: