ntal in Costa Rica cost?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rental cars in Costa Rica are significantly more expensive than in the US or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a>. Especially if you rent a car for just yourself, it&#x2019;ll add up. It&#x2019;s best to split the costs with a group of people when you plan on visiting multiple locations, as this is more favorable than going everywhere by bus. The total price of the rental typically depends on a few things; the time of the year you&#x2019;re renting, the duration of your trip, the type of car, and the type of insurance.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"surfing costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"surfing costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78881 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143951\/camping-costa-rica-16-614x768.jpg 614w, https