 you to compare options.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car in Costa Rica via <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You won&#x2019;t find any rental agencies at the small airports of San Jos&#xE9; or Liberia Guanacaste, but there are some a couple of kilometers away. However, despite these agencies not actually being at the airport, they will include a so-called &#x2018;airport tax&#x2019; on top of your rental. Cars rented &#x2018;from the airport&#x2019; are subject to an additional government-imposed tax of 13 &#x2013; 14% of the total cost of the rental. If you can, avoid renting from places close to the airport to avoid this extra cost.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to rent a car? Requirements Is it easy to drive? Tips for renting Price for a rental car Where to rent a car? How to rent a car in Costa Rica The advantage of renting a car in Costa Rica is obvious; you can go where you want at your own pace, without being [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":87272,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_rel